source.name: Schedule Sales Query Report Generation System
source.description: Schedule Sales Query presents sales volume figures as reported to GSA by contractors. The reports are generated as quarterly reports for the current year and the past five fiscal years. The sales data reported here are updated as contractors' reports are received, but the data may not be up to date as adjustments can be received at any time. The information on this site mirrors the data used by GSA for contract administration and fee management. It is not the official source of sales data. This data should be used for informational purposes only.
